para_trans: Rural Hospital with a capacity of 30 beds at Jalgaon Jamod, District Buldhana
About upgradation of 100 bedded Sub District Hospital.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2022 / Q. No.263 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Commissionerate of Health Services, Mumbai. No. AASE / Room 3 / T-7 / Jalgaon Jamod
100 of a 30 bedded rural hospital at Jalgaon Jamod, District Buldhana
A proposal to upgrade the bedded sub-district hospital was under consideration of the government.
100 of a 30 bedded rural hospital at Jalgaon Jamod, District Buldhana
The government has decided to upgrade the bedded sub-district hospital as a "special case."
Approval is being given. By acquiring the space for the hospital in this category in the prescribed manner.
Construction and post-production will be dealt with separately.
This Government decision is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
